{% comment %}
  Guest Recommendation - shared context.

  Surfaces one recommendation (amenity, feature, or nearby attraction) per render,
  chosen from the `recommendations` list. The list is plain JSON the operator edits
  in plugin settings (static_data) / tmp/data.json locally - add and remove freely.

  Selection is time-seeded so each device refresh rotates to a different card, with
  no JS needed (server-side Liquid renders cleanly to the e-ink image). Matching
  line art for each card is inlined as a stroke-only SVG, which stays crisp on
  1-bit / 2-bit grayscale. Every id is per-instance, so the plugin is mashup-safe.
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} ---------- Title bar toggle (string- or boolean-backed select) ---------- {% endcomment %}
{% assign gr_show_title_bar_raw = trmnl.plugin_settings.custom_fields_values.show_title_bar | default: "true" %}
{% assign gr_show_title_bar = true %}
{% if gr_show_title_bar_raw == "false" or gr_show_title_bar_raw == false or gr_show_title_bar_raw == "no" %}
  {% assign gr_show_title_bar = false %}
{% endif %}

{% assign gr_site_name = "radretreat.com" %}

{% comment %} ---------- Pick one recommendation ----------
  Seed off the render time so the card rotates every refresh. Fall back to the
  Liquid "now" filter when the system timestamp is unavailable (local preview).
  The prime multiplier spreads consecutive seeds across the list. {% endcomment %}
{% assign gr_count = recommendations | size %}
{% assign gr_index = 0 %}
{% if gr_count > 0 %}
  {% assign gr_seed = trmnl.system.timestamp_utc | plus: 0 %}
  {% if gr_seed == 0 %}{% assign gr_seed = "now" | date: "%s" | plus: 0 %}{% endif %}
  {% assign gr_index = gr_seed | times: 7919 | modulo: gr_count %}
{% endif %}

{% assign gr_icon = "palm" %}
{% assign gr_tag = "" %}
{% assign gr_title = "" %}
{% assign gr_body = "" %}
{% if gr_count > 0 %}
  {% for r in recommendations %}
    {% if forloop.index0 == gr_index %}
      {% assign gr_icon = r.icon | default: "palm" %}
      {% assign gr_tag = r.tag | default: "" %}
      {% assign gr_title = r.title | default: "" %}
      {% assign gr_body = r.body | default: "" %}
      {% break %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% comment %}
  ---------- Icon ----------
  Recognizable, professional icons sourced from the Iconify project (the same
  catalog iconbuddy.com uses): mostly Font Awesome 6 Solid, plus lineicons
  (surfboard) and Game Icons (disc-golf basket, palm). All are single-path,
  filled, MIT / CC-licensed glyphs drawn with currentColor, so the layout
  controls the shade and they threshold to solid black on 1-bit / 2-bit e-ink.
  Each glyph keeps its own viewBox and fills its container (aspect preserved).
  To swap an icon, replace the SVG in the matching {% raw %}{% when %}{% endraw %} branch.
{% endcomment %}
{% capture gr_icon_markup %}
{% case gr_icon %}
